Package gameMain.mainMenu

Class MainMenuFactory

java.lang.Object
gameMain.mainMenu.MainMenuFactory
public class MainMenuFactory
extends java.lang.Object
Factory of the Main Menu Screen (FlyWeight Pattern). Responsible for reducing the number of objects by only creating the MVC of the game if there isn't any duplicated.
